          <title>Victor Wembanyama expected to miss remainder of season after blood clot diagnosis, Spurs announce</title>
          <description><![CDATA[San Antonio Spurs star Victor Wembanyama is expected to miss the remainder of the NBA regular season after being diagnosed with a blood clot in his right shoulder, the Spurs announced Thursday. It's a massive blow to the Spurs, who are contending for a playoff spot in the Western Conference.]]></description>
